videos.headline: Harden's first Nets points come at the line

videos.description: James Harden cruises in for a Eurostep layup and a few possessions later, drives his way to the bucket for another shot.

videos.headline: Harden's behind-the-back dime leads to Green's 3-pointer

videos.description: James Harden creates some space between a defender and knocks down a 3-pointer.

videos.description: James Harden impresses in his Nets debut with 32 points, 14 assists and 12 rebounds.
